     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d064n3-ptr" id="PJA04d064n3">3</a>
      
   <p>Articles of War, LXVI (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington C. Ford and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress&lt;/i&gt;, 17741789, Washington, 19041937; 34 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 2:122).</p>

